## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="647ea-102">次の表は、現在サポートされているオプションを示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-102">The following table shows the currently supported options.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="647ea-103">カテゴリ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-103">Category</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="647ea-104">設定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-104">Setting</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="647ea-105">値/効果</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-105">Value/effect</span></span>|  
|--------------|-------------|-------------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="647ea-106">コントラクト</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-106">contract</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="647ea-107">継承</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-107">inheritance</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="647ea-108">`true` コントラクトの継承を有効にするには`false`をオフにします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-108">`true` to turn contract inheritance on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="647ea-109">既定値は、`true` です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-109">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="647ea-110">ランタイム</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-110">runtime</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="647ea-111">チェック</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-111">checking</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="647ea-112">`true` 実行時チェック; を有効にするには`false`をオフにします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-112">`true` to turn run-time checking on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="647ea-113">既定値は、`true` です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-113">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="647ea-114">次の例に示すように、この属性を使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-114">You can use this attribute as illustrated in the following examples.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="647ea-115">ランタイムがアセンブリ全体のチェックをオフにします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-115">To turn off run-time checking for the entire assembly:</span></span>  
  
```  
[assembly:ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="647ea-116">有効にするランタイム コントラクト チェック、特定の種類。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-116">To turn run-time contract checking on for a specific type:</span></span>  
  
```  
   [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", true)]  
   class TypeWithRuntimeChecking {  
  
       ...  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="647ea-117">実行時のチェックをオフに特定のメソッド。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="647ea-117">To turn run-time checking off for a specific method:</span></span>  
  
```  
// Turn off all contract inheritance from interface IList<T>  
[ContractOption("contract", "inheritance", false)]  
class MyConcurrentList<T> : IList<T> {  
   ...  
}  
  
[ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
public override MyMethod(int x) {  
   // no inherited contracts checked at runtime,  
   // no invariants checked at runtime.  
   ...  
}  
  
       [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
       public void MethodWithoutRuntimeChecking(...) {  
          ...  
       }  
   }  
  
```
